trans-unit.source: Represents a converter that converts the dimensions of a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox"></xref> control into a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en konverterare som konverterar dimensioner för en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox"> </xref> -kontrollen i en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush> created by this converter applies an <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.OpacityMask%2A> to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Border> of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox> so that it does not appear in the area defined for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush>skapas i den här konverteraren gäller en <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.OpacityMask%2A>till <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Border>av den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox>så att den inte visas i det område som definierats för den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A>i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Border> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement.OpacityMask%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush>

trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.BorderGapMaskConverter"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Creates a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush"></xref> that draws the border for a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush"> </xref> som ritar kantlinjen för en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The three numbers that are in the `values` parameter represent the following <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox> control parameters: - The width of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox> <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> content.
trans-unit.target: Tre siffror som finns i den `values` parametern representerar följande <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox>styr parametrarna:-bredden på de <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox> <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A>innehåll.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox>
